        <p class="lead text-muted">Gain practical engineering experience with City Building Engineering's Academic Internship Program in Kigali, Rwanda. Combine software training with real project work under professional supervision.</p>
        <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
            <i class="bi bi-envelope"></i> Apply Now
          </a>
          <a href="https://wa.me/250789257758?text=Hello%20City%20Building!%20I%27m%20interested%20in%20the%20Academic%20Internship%20program." target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">
            <i class="bi bi-whatsapp"></i> Chat on WhatsApp
